# Group user

## user's Requests [/user]

### Get Posts [GET /user/post]
+ Request
    + Attributes
        + coordinates : `[100 , 5]` (array) - youser coordinates [latitude , longtude]
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[Post])

### Create Posts [POST /user/createpost]
+ Request
    + Attributes
        + user : `58cf9a3a3ca5d434952d6999` (string) - The user's id
        + coordinates : `[100 , 5]` (array) - [longtude , latitude]
        + content : `hello world` (string) - the content of the post
        + tags : `['music' , 'sports']` (array) - array of tags
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Post)

### DELETE Posts [DELETE /user/post]
+ Request
    + Attributes
        + post : `58cf9a3a3ca5d434952d6999` (string) - The post's id
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + numOfLikes : `22` (number) - number of likes for the deleted post
        + numOfComments : `22` (number) - number of comments for the deleted post
        + post(Post)

### UPDATE Posts [PUT /user/post]
+ Request
    + Attributes
        + post : `58cf9a3a3ca5d434952d6999` (string) - The post's id
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Post)

### like&unlike Posts [PUT /user/like]
+ Request
    + Attributes
        + post : `58cf9a3a3ca5d434952d6999` (string) - The post's id
        + user : `58cf9a3a3ca5d434952d6999` (string) - The user's id
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + likes : `12` (number) - the number of likes
        + like : `true` (boolean) - like or not

### Add Comments [POST /user/comment]
+ Request
    + Attributes
        + user : `58cf9a3a3ca5d434952d6999` (string) - The user's id
        + post : `58cf9a3a3ca5d434952d6999` (string) - The post's id
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Comment)
        + date : `2017-07-06T10:39:43.788Z` (string) - the comment creation date

### Edit a Comment [PUT /user/comment]
+ Request
    + Attributes
        +
+ Response 200 (application/json)

