## Data Structures

### Post
+ user : `58cf9a3a3ca5d434952d6999` (string) - The user's id
+ likesCounter : `58` (number) - the number of likes
+ commentsCounter : `58` (number) - the number of comments
+ coordinates : 100 , 5 (array) - [longtude , latitude]
+ date : `2017-07-06T10:39:43.788Z` (string) - the post creation date
+ content : `hello world` (string) - the content of the post
+ tags : music , sports (array) - array of tags

### Comment
+ user : `58cf9a3a3ca5d434952d6999` (string) - The user's id
+ post : `58cf9a3a3ca5d434952d6999` (string) - The post's id
+ content : `some comment` (string) - the content of coment
